room_title: Escape room "Tony's Bistro" by ESCAPE:chandler in Phoenix
room_address: 312 N Alma School Rd, Suite 9, Chandler, AZ 85224
room_description:
Italian Bistro owner Tony Rigatoni turned to notorious mob hit-man Rocco Calzone looking for a little help taking care of a few high-profile pests if you know what I mean.
When the job was done, the feds were waiting and now Rocco is in the slammer… and he’s giving names. That can't stand!
​
You got word that the money that was supposed to go to Rocco is still inside Tony's Bistro and you have just one hour to get in there and get it back before the feds come for it, and for YOU. After you get the cash, it's payback time!
